metadata.description:
《The Sun - THE PRINCE 王子》


ZAI 在

Power:  
*Infinite & unconditional love.  
*Ability to dissolve illusions effortlessly.  
*Sparks celebration of life.  
*Love leadership

Story:  
Zai is a young prince that is into the magical arts. Despite his royal duties & expectations from the family & the society, he stayed true to who he was; an artist & found his way through the mysteries of the unknown & eventually awakened to his inner wisdom & magic that is infinite & eternal. Brought forth a new kingdom with different realities. 

Message: 
Listen to the whispers of your heart, be true to who you are; for you are the one you’ve been looking for. 

Let the universe flow through you, sing through you & dance with you. Be the hero of your own story.
